<template>
  <v-form ref="formRegister" @submit.prevent="login" lazy-validation>
    <v-container>
        <v-row>
        <v-col>
                <v-text-field
                v-model="username"
                label="UsuÃ¡rio"
                :rules="this.rulesUsername"
                hide-details="auto"
                ></v-text-field>
                <v-text-field v-model="password" :rules="rulesPassword" label="Senha"></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        </v-row>
      <v-row>
        <v-col>
            <v-btn
                block
                color="primary"
                elevation="4"
                v-on:click="seila"
            >Login</v-btn>
        </v-col>
        </v-row>
    </v-container>
  </v-form>
</template>

<script>


export default {
  name: 'Register',

    data() {
        return {
            username: '',
            password: '',
            rulesUsername: [
                value => !!value || 'Required.',
            ],
            rulesPassword: [
                value => !!value || 'Required.',
                value => (value && value.length >= 8) || 'Min 8 characters',
            ],
        }
    },
    methods: {
        seila() {
            console.log(this);
        },
    },

};
</script>
